# Write your MySQL query statement below

select user_id ,concat(upper(substring(name,1,1)), lower(substring(name,2,length(name)-1)))as name from Users order by user_id 

Input: 
Users table:
+---------+-------+
| user_id | name  |
+---------+-------+
| 1       | aLice |
| 2       | bOB   |
+---------+-------+
Output: 
+---------+-------+
| user_id | name  |
+---------+-------+
| 1       | Alice |
| 2       | Bob   |
+---------+-------+
